A '''National Depository Centre''' is a [[public library]] in [[India]] which receives a copy of all books, newspapers and periodicals published in the country with ISBN and ISSN as the case may be.<ref name="ministryofculture">http://www.indiaculture.nic.in/indiaculture/nl_dbact.htm</ref> There are four centres:
*[[Connemara Public Library]] in [[Chennai]] *[[Asiatic Society of Bombay]] in [[Mumbai]] *[[National Library of India|National Library, Calcutta]] *[[Delhi Public Library|Delhi Public Library, Delhi]]
